#

Avocado Lime Dip

10 min
$3.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

DipSnackEasyFresh

Description

A creamy, zesty dip bursting with fresh avocado and lime flavor, perfect for pairing with chips or vegetables.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 1 clove, minced
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cilantro: 2 tablespoons, chopped (optional)
